The '''Keiffler Brothers''' were a tech crew that operated from [[Pembric II]] during the early years of the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]]. They were contracted to work for [[Moff/Legends|Moff]] [[Kentor Sarne]] on [[Kal'Shebbol/Legends|Kal'Shebbol]], and, among other projects, designed many of the programming trapdoors that infested the systems of the [[CR90 corvette/Legends|CR90 corvette]] ''[[FarStar]]''. They were considered the best slicers in the [[Kathol sector/Legends|Kathol sector]]. The Brothers never returned to Pembric II, and had been killed by Sarne's forces after completing their work.

